{
  "stem": "3848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't stop, because that same train-- I couldn't get off to see who was there in the city, because I wasn't going to go to the city.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was going to go to Poland and Rowne was Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we continued, unfortunately, further and we came into Poland, somewhere not far from Krakow, we crossed the border.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Polish soldiers greeted us, and the first thing we found out was anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They spoke in Polish, which I understood very well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to say in Polish, oh zyd, zyd.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you-- we understood what it was and didn't care for us, didn't care for us at all--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--that we were coming back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were saying that they weren't happy to see Jews coming from Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't they stay there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we came back, actually not to stay in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We figured we were going to go someplace else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From that place, they sent us into Poland, into areas where they could put us, and we went to [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oberschlasing. ?] It was sort of-- it used to be a German section of Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I landed in a city called Bytom-- Beuthen in German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as we were opening up the cars, there was a group of Zionist people from Israel came to recruit us to an organization-- to a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And anybody that was young-- I was probably about-- 1946-- I was 23 years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us-- they asked if I wanted to join the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, sure, I'm all alone, I have no family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, why not?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took my suitcase, whatever I had there, took it right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
